title: Bug 118780 - Incorrect column names shown in expression builder when selecting dataset
OB: When selecting a dataset in the expression builder and double clicking on the first column name, the original column name is displayed instead of the alias name.
EB: According to scr 78193 in the tracker, the first column in the expression builder should display the alias name instead of the original column name.
SR:
1. Open the expression builder.
2. Select the desired dataset.
3. Double click on the first column name.
4. Observe that the original column name is displayed instead of the alias name.
